summary: This mod add a new Player Home! It\'s a starter Shack lokated in Riverwood!
descriptionHtml:
This mod add a new Player Home! It\'s a starter Shack lokated in Riverwood!

Version: 2.0

Futures:
-No load Doors
-Starter Shack
-Near the River
-Dragons can land on your Shack
-Own Map Marker called \"My Shack\"
-A bed

Futures (2.0):
-Dim the Lights
-Add a Barrel in front of door
-Add a Cellar to the Shack
-Add a Tanning Rack
-Remove some ugly Grass grown throw floor
-Add some small accessory in and around the Shack


I hope you like it!
author: Stormbow123
